      "message": "Line 274: Invalid or unsupported peer input is silently ignored all the way down the stack. That makes caller bugs hard to diagnose and hides why an on-demand sync did not happen. Please log at least the invalid/empty normalized peer case in `ConversationModule::syncConversationsWith`, consistent with existing JAMI logging patterns, rather than returning silently.",
